      <div type="commentary">
        <head>Commentary</head>
        <p>See discussion at <xref type="eAla-text" n="VII.17">VII.17</xref>.</p>
      </div>

      <div type="history" n="locations"><head>Locations</head><p><rs type="found"><rs type="monuList">City, South-west</rs>: lying on the surface of a ploughed field just inside the south-east stretch of the city walls.</rs>. <rs type="origLocation"><seg cert="low">An unidentified church</seg></rs>. <rs type="lastLocation">Findspot.</rs>. </p></div>

      

      

